class dataflow_demo.servers.data_server.data_source_rpc.DataSource.Processor(handler)¶

Bases: dataflow_demo.servers.data_server.data_source_rpc.DataSource.Iface, thrift.Thrift.TProcessor

process(iprot, oprot)¶

Process a request. The normal behvaior is to have the processor invoke the correct handler and then it is the server’s responsibility to write the response to oprot.
